                {
                  "id": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3nk36r45/manifest/annotation/p3",
                  "type": "Annotation",
                  "motivation": "commenting",
                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p>testimonials, <add>?</add>\n                                        <hi rend=\"underline\">two</hi> from the<lb/> Director of the\n                                        Hebrew National Insti=<lb/>=tution since my resignation.</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(1)\">Synagogue affairs in\n                                                  <placeName>Jamaica</placeName><lb/>—I regret to\n                                        state—are not in a<lb/> flourishing condition. There\n                                        seems<lb/> to be a feeling rising in\n                                                  <placeName>Falmouth</placeName><lb/> to establish\n                                        a synagogue there. The<lb/> Jewish Community in that town\n                                        numbers<lb/> about Seventy Souls who are, with<lb/> scarcely\n                                        an exception, in good circum=<lb/>=stances. Perhaps you will\n                                        lend your<lb/> pen towards stimulating them in the<lb/>\n                                        “good <sic>cauce</sic>.”</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(1)\">The administration for the<lb/> “School” lately\n                                        elected is</p>\n                              <list type=\"simple\">\n                                        <head/>\n                                        <item rend=\"indent(2)\"><persName>P\n                                                  Laurence</persName>   President</item>\n                                        <item rend=\"indent(2)\"><persName>G\n                                                  Delgado</persName>   Vice</item>\n                                        <item rend=\"indent(2)\"><persName>Alex\n                                                  Aria</persName>     Treas.</item>\n                              </list>\n                              <p/>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(1)\">The number of Directors not being<lb/> yet\n                                        complete, I am unable to send<lb/> you a perfect list. I\n                                        will however<lb/> do so at a future period (Dr.)</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(5)\">With best wishes.</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(6)\">Believe me</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(7)\">Yours Very Truly</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(7)\"><persName role=\"author\">Henry S.\n                                        Jacobs</persName>.</p>\n                    </body>\n          </text>\n</TEI>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3nk36r45/canvas/p3"
                }
              ]
            }
